# Mac filesystem metadata
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor / IDE artifacts
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Python bytecode cache (from the optional bundled _scripts/ tooling)
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Obsidian workspace state (personal UI state, not study content)
.obsidian/workspace*
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/graph.json

# OS / network artifacts
Thumbs.db
.directory

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Personal study work — excluded by default so this folder can be shared
# without leaking your private session history. If you want to keep your
# OWN study work in version control (recommended for personal use), edit
# this section: remove the exclusions you want tracked, or maintain a
# private fork with your study work checked in.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

# State files: live record of where you are in each subject
**/_state.md

# User profile (optional, may contain personal preferences)
_USER.md

# Personal cartridges — anything NOT prefixed `Example-Subject-` is treated
# as a personal study cartridge by default and excluded.
# To track your own cartridge, either:
#   1. Remove the broad rule below and add specific exclusions for
#      Sessions/, Quizzes/, etc. that you want kept private, OR
#   2. Use `git add -f` on the specific cartridge folder.

# Session logs and quiz history (personal record of study)
**/Sessions/*.md
!**/Sessions/.gitkeep

**/Quizzes/Socratic-Conceptual/*.md
!**/Quizzes/Socratic-Conceptual/.gitkeep

**/Quizzes/SR-Performance-Log/*.md
!**/Quizzes/SR-Performance-Log/Phase-1-SR-Log.md
!**/Quizzes/SR-Performance-Log/.gitkeep

# Synthesis drafts (personal writing)
**/Synthesis/Weekly-Journals/*.md
!**/Synthesis/Weekly-Journals/.gitkeep

**/Synthesis/Monthly-Essays/*.md
!**/Synthesis/Monthly-Essays/.gitkeep

**/Synthesis/Phase-End-Translations/*.md
!**/Synthesis/Phase-End-Translations/.gitkeep

**/Synthesis/Quarterly-Drafts/*.md
!**/Synthesis/Quarterly-Drafts/.gitkeep

# SR card files (if user stores cards in dedicated files vs embedded in atoms)
**/SR-Cards/*.md
!**/SR-Cards/.gitkeep
# Anki export artifacts (regenerated on demand; never tracked)
**/SR-Cards/*.tsv

# Capture layer (personal fleeting notes / triage inbox)
# The OV-root inbox: ignore captures, keep the folder + its README.
_Inbox/*.md
!_Inbox/README.md
!_Inbox/.gitkeep
# Per-subject capture pens
**/Captures/*.md
!**/Captures/.gitkeep

# Insight ledger (personal, decision-grade learning records)
**/Insights/*.md
!**/Insights/.gitkeep

# Lesson artifacts (personal produced output — markdown source + optional rendered HTML)
**/Lessons/*.md
**/Lessons/*.html
!**/Lessons/.gitkeep

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Always tracked (overrides the above for the example cartridge):
# The shipped example cartridge demonstrates the system; its bootstrap
# session log, seed atoms, example captures, and example insight are part of the release.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
!Example-Subject-*/Sessions/*BOOTSTRAP*.md
!Example-Subject-*/_state.md
!Example-Subject-*/Captures/*.md
!Example-Subject-*/Insights/*.md
!Example-Subject-*/Lessons/*.md
!Example-Subject-*/Lessons/*.html
